sequenceDiagram
    participant Kafka as Kafka Broker<br/>9092/TCP SASL_SSL
    participant Processor as kafka-processor<br/>(Python CLI - Dev Only)
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>data/ directory
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>(Konflux Build)
    participant Operator as model-registry-operator
    participant Init as Init Container<br/>odh-model-performance-data
    participant Volume as Shared Volume<br/>(emptyDir)
    participant Catalog as model-catalog<br/>Container

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Kafka,FS: Flow 1: Kafka CDC Ingestion (Development Only)
        Kafka->>Processor: CDC messages (Debezium/simple format)<br/>SASL_SSL / SCRAM-SHA-512
        Processor->>Processor: Entity detection<br/>(topic → type → heuristic)
        Processor->>Processor: Field mapping +<br/>post-processing transforms
        Processor->>FS: Write JSON/NDJSON files<br/>provider/model/ hierarchy
    end

    rect rgb(224, 242, 255)
        Note over FS,Registry: Build Phase (Konflux CI)
        FS->>Registry: docker build<br/>COPY data/ → /app/benchmarks<br/>UBI9-minimal base
    end

    rect rgb(224, 255, 224)
        Note over Operator,Catalog: Flow 2: Data Container Init (Production)
        Operator->>Operator: Patches model-catalog deployment<br/>with init container image ref
        Init->>Volume: Copy /app/benchmarks/*<br/>to shared volume
        Note over Init: Init container completes<br/>and exits
        Volume->>Catalog: model-catalog reads<br/>benchmark data from volume
        Note over Catalog: Serves benchmark data<br/>to API consumers
    end
